{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/40065", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/40065/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/40065/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/40065/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/40065", "id": 209848162, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyMDk4NDgxNjI=", "number": 40065, "title": "rustdoc creates test in tmpdir, which is noexec on some systems", "user": {"login": "chifflier", "id": 308574, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMwODU3NA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/308574?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier", "html_url": "https://github.com/chifflier", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chifflier/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 203738, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMDM3Mzg=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/T-rustdoc", "name": "T-rustdoc", "color": "bfd4f2", "default": false, "description": "Relevant to the rustdoc team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue."}, {"id": 630652267, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2MzA2NTIyNjc=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-feature-request", "name": "C-feature-request", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: A feature request, i.e: not implemented / a PR."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 7, "created_at": "2017-02-23T18:43:01Z", "updated_at": "2022-12-11T02:22:50Z", "closed_at": "2021-07-02T10:32:13Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "When running `cargo test` to run unit tests, the documentation tests are executed from `/tmp`, which is mounted as noexec on many distros (for security reasons).\r\nThis does not happen for other unit tests (using the `test` attribute), because they are build in `target/<build type>`.\r\n\r\nSuggested solution: build documentation tests in the same directory ?\r\n\r\nExample code:\r\n```\r\n/// ```\r\n///\r\n/// # fn main() { test1 () }\r\npub fn test1() {\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd mount `/tmp` as noexec:\r\n```\r\nmount -o remount,noexec /tmp\r\n```\r\n\r\n(reopening here as requested in  https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/issues/3756)", "closed_by": {"login": "jyn514", "id": 23638587, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIzNjM4NTg3", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/23638587?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514", "html_url": "https://github.com/jyn514", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"